        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/tBJiY143HHghE5Os0FCjaCn6/image.png\">image.png</a><br>\nAre there any pre-defined matrix norms in mathlib4 as defined in the figure? Or how should I define it?</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/tBJiY143HHghE5Os0FCjaCn6/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img data-original-content-type=\"image/png\" data-original-dimensions=\"561x91\" src=\"/user_uploads/thumbnail/3121/tBJiY143HHghE5Os0FCjaCn6/image.png/840x560.webp\"></a></div>",
